@startuml
title 图6-3 流程启动与状态写回时序图

actor 用户
participant "业务页面/审批中心" as Page
participant "PostgREST" as Api
participant "workflow.start_workflow_instance" as StartFn
participant "workflow.transition_workflow_instance" as TransitionFn
participant "workflow.can_execute_task" as CheckFn
database "workflow.instances" as Instances
database "workflow.task_approvals" as Approvals
database "app_center.workflow_state_mappings" as Mappings
database "业务表/草稿表" as Biz

用户 -> Page : 发起流程或执行审批
Page -> Api : POST /rpc/workflow.start_workflow_instance
Api -> StartFn : 创建流程实例
StartFn -> Instances : 写入初始实例状态
StartFn --> Api : 返回实例编号
Api --> Page : 返回流程实例

用户 -> Page : 提交审批意见/下一节点
Page -> Api : POST /rpc/workflow.transition_workflow_instance
Api -> TransitionFn : 推进流程实例
TransitionFn -> CheckFn : 校验当前用户是否可执行任务
CheckFn --> TransitionFn : 返回 true/false
alt 无执行权限
TransitionFn --> Api : 返回权限异常
Api --> Page : 提示无权审批
else 允许推进
TransitionFn -> Instances : 更新 current_task_id/status
TransitionFn -> Approvals : 写入审批记录
TransitionFn -> Mappings : 读取节点到业务状态的映射
TransitionFn -> Biz : 回写业务状态字段
TransitionFn --> Api : 返回更新后的实例
Api --> Page : 返回审批结果
end

@enduml
